data.description: One owner home on just under an acre in Doe Valley.  Home was recently updated in 2019 with a new roof, granite countertops, LVP flooring and partial new deck in 2023.   Three doors to enter this home show the openness of the living room, dining area and kitchen.  There are 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom on the main floor.  Upstairs is the master suite, to include its own balcony, generous size master bedroom, bathroom with a walk in shower and a walk in closet.  In the basement, you'll find a room that can be used as a family room with an electric fireplace as well as an additional room.  There is a storage room that contains the back up generator panel (Fridge, Microwave, Furnace, Master bedroom and the red room).  Laundry area is also in the basement.
